    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="875296233">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-875296233" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-875296233" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="875296233">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2851582/">freeman1003</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-12-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作者以前的作品《雪白雪红》让人印象深刻，因此慕名将这套书（上下两册）买来。不过读完，倒是较为失望，人物写得不够传神生动，而且人物之间的关系也没有梳理清楚。本以为这套书能够帮助自己理清四野这一最大的山头的来龙去脉，但最后还是一团麻！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="472609249">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-472609249" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-472609249" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="472609249">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/MoonDark/">月黑风高</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-07-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
